* anisotropic_cloud_scattering Added to `Radtrans` arguments and to attributes. Calculation mode of cloud scattering, can be True, False, or 'auto' (default); in 'auto' mode, cloud scattering is calculated depending on whether an emission (True) or transmission spectrum (False) is calculated; a warning is displayed if the "wrong" mode is chosen
